title_bed_bats_review: Rental unit in Siliguri · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 1 bath
listing_description:
Welcome to our luxurious guest house, located just 7 minutes away from NJP railway station. We are thrilled to offer you a private room, while also offering you access to our shared living room and dining space. In terms of amenities, we have thoughtfully included a hot bath tub.

Aside from your private room, you will also have access to our shared living room and dining space.

We look forward to hosting you. Make your stay with us a truly remarkable one.

Warm regards,
Nirajeeta Chowdhury
